@node intro "Information"

	Amiga. Music. Replayer. Intros. Demos.

	If any of those above words don't say anything to you, maybe you
	have downloaded and unpacked wrong archive. =)

	@{i}Ok, to be short and simple:@{ui} @{b}this is a music replayer called BMOD@{ub}.
	It has been coded from the dust, taking some examples from
	ProTracker© sourcecode (but not coded the same way) and from
	The Player 6.1A, and BMOD has become faster than many other
	replayer available for Amiga.

	This release is a ŖETA, so these documents may be more and less
	incomplete and inaccurate. Source code may contain many bugs
	and misbehaviors.
	At this time, only documents which are complete and accurate,
	are history and bugs. =)
	But the time will reveal will this player get off its
	baby shoes, and conquer the world of Amiga users. =8Q..

	If you are still interested about BMOD, good. Then I know that
	my work with this beast has not gone waste.
@endnode

